---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sprocket ‚Äî POS & Payments for Bike Shops"
  description="Sprocket is payment and invoicing software built exclusively for independent bike shops. Repair orders, deposits, SMS updates, and transparent pricing ‚Äî self-serve in 20 minutes."
  ogUrl="https://sprocketpos.com"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="inline-block bg-[#fef9e7] text-[#f97316] text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">
        Now accepting early access
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#4d9078] max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
        Payments. Invoices. Repair orders. Built for bike shops.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#6b7280] max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">
        Lightspeed is for chains. Square is for coffee shops. Sprocket is for your shop ‚Äî self-serve setup, transparent pricing, and a repair workflow that actually makes sense.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a
          href="/waitlist"
          class="bg-[#4d9078] text-white rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-[#4d9078]/90"
        >
          Join the waitlist
        </a>
        <a
          href="#pricing"
          class="bg-white text-[#4d9078] border border-[#4d9078] rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-[#f9fafb]"
        >
          See pricing
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280] mt-4">No demo call. No sales pitch. Live in 20 minutes.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-0 mt-8 text-sm text-[#6b7280]">
        <span class="px-4">Self-serve setup</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#e5e7eb]">|</span>
        <span class="px-4">Transparent pricing</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#e5e7eb]">|</span>
        <span class="px-4">Built for repairs</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section id="features" class="bg-[#f9fafb] py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="text-[#f97316] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Features</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078] mt-2">Everything a bike shop actually needs.</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-2">Not a retail POS with repairs bolted on. Built from the bench up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üîß</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078] mb-2">Repair Orders, Done Right</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Create a ticket, collect a deposit, update the status, send the final invoice ‚Äî all in one place. No spreadsheets. No sticky notes. No "where's that repair order?" ever again.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üí≥</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078] mb-2">Deposits & Partial Billing</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            High-ticket rebuild? Custom build? Collect a deposit upfront, bill progress payments, and close out the final balance. Sprocket tracks the outstanding amount the whole way through.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üì±</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078] mb-2">SMS Status Updates</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "Is my bike ready?" Stop answering that call. Sprocket automatically texts your customer when their repair moves stages ‚Äî received, in progress, ready for pickup. Included in every plan.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078] mb-2">Pricing That Makes Sense</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6b7280] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            No per-location surprise fees. No "call us for pricing." No annual contract lock-in. Sprocket is $49/mo to start and everything is on the pricing page. Go live in 20 minutes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="text-[#f97316] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Early Feedback</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078] mt-2">Shops that get it.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "I spent three years duct-taping Square and a Google Sheet together. Sprocket replaced both in an afternoon. I don't know why I waited."
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[#4d9078]">Marcus T.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280]">Ridgeline Bikes, Denver CO</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#6b7280]/60 mt-1 italic">Fictional review</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "My mechanics update repair tickets from their phones. My customers get texts when their bike is ready. I get about 10 fewer calls a day. That alone is worth it."
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[#4d9078]">Jenny K.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280]">Spoke & Pedal, Austin TX</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#6b7280]/60 mt-1 italic">Fictional review</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "Lightspeed wanted $400 a month and a 45-minute demo before they'd even tell me the price. Sprocket had me up and running before lunch."
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[#4d9078]">Dave R.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280]">High Gear Cycles, Portland OR</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#6b7280]/60 mt-1 italic">Fictional review</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section class="bg-[#f9fafb] py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="text-[#f97316] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Comparison</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078] mt-2">Finally, software that fits.</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-2">See how Sprocket compares to the alternatives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-[#4d9078] text-white">
                <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Feature</th>
                <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Sprocket</th>
                <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Lightspeed</th>
                <th class="text-left px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Square</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Repair order workflow</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ Built-in</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ö†Ô∏è Add-on</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Deposit + partial billing</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ Built-in</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ö†Ô∏è Complex setup</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">SMS customer updates</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ Included</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ö†Ô∏è Paid add-on</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Transparent pricing</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ On the website</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå Call for pricing</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚úÖ</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Self-serve onboarding</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ 20 minutes</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå Demo required</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚úÖ</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Built for bike shops</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">‚úÖ Only this</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ö†Ô∏è Retail-first</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">‚ùå Generic</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-gray-100">
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Starting price</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#4d9078]">$49/mo</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">~$149/mo+</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">2.6% + fees only</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section id="pricing" class="bg-white py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="text-[#f97316] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Pricing</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078] mt-2">Simple, honest pricing.</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6b7280] mt-2">No surprise fees. No annual contracts. Cancel any time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto items-start">
        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078]">Starter</h3>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078]">$49</span>
            <span class="text-[#6b7280]">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280] mt-1">For solo operators just getting started.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#111827]">
            <li>‚Ä¢ POS + payment processing</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Repair order management</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Basic invoicing</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ 1 location</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Email support</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/waitlist"
            class="block text-center mt-6 border border-[#4d9078] text-[#4d9078] rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-[#f9fafb]"
          >
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pro -->
        <div class="bg-[#4d9078] rounded-lg p-6 text-white shadow-lg md:scale-105">
          <span class="inline-block bg-[#f4d35e] text-[#111827] text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full mb-2">
            Most popular
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Pro</h3>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold">$99</span>
            <span class="text-white/70">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-1">For shops ready to run a tighter operation.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-white">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Everything in Starter</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ SMS status updates (included)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Deposit + partial billing</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Recurring service plans</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Advanced reporting</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Up to 3 locations</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/waitlist"
            class="block text-center mt-6 bg-white text-[#4d9078] rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-white/90"
          >
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Scale -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#4d9078]">Scale</h3>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#4d9078]">$199</span>
            <span class="text-[#6b7280]">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7280] mt-1">For multi-location shops that need more.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#111827]">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Everything in Pro</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Unlimited locations</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ API access</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Priority support</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Custom onboarding</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/waitlist"
            class="block text-center mt-6 border border-[#4d9078] text-[#4d9078] rounded-lg px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-[#f9fafb]"
          >
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#4d9078] py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Built for your shop. Ready when you are.</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 mt-3">Join the waitlist and get locked-in early access pricing.</p>
      <a
        href="/waitlist"
        class="inline-block mt-8 bg-white text-[#4d9078] rounded-lg px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white/90"
      >
        Reserve your spot
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-4">No demo call. No credit card. 60 seconds to sign up.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
